$ rule (properties of bulk)
    (
        - sentence properties of $x : $( $prop : $value )+
    )
    (
        $( 
            $value is $prop of $x
        )+
    )

properties of apple:
    color: red
    description: (a bright, fresh apple)
    (initial appearance): apple
    article: an

$ facts
$ assert red is color of apple
$ assert apple is (initial appearance) of apple
$ assert an is article of apple
$ assert (a bright, fresh apple) is description of apple